\begin_inset Formula $A_{\tau+1}=\frac{1-a_{\tau}+b_{\rho}+a_{\tau}-1}{1-a_{\tau}}A_{\tau}(1+r)+\frac{b_{\rho}}{1-a_{\tau}}\delta_{\tau+1}=(1+\frac{b_{\rho}+a_{\tau}-1}{1-a_{\tau}})(1+r)A_{\tau}+\frac{b_{\rho}}{1-a_{\tau}}\delta_{\tau+1}$
